Dear Kaustabh,

I am pleased to inform you that your profile has been shortlisted for the
Forward Deployed Engineer, GenAI role.

We are now ready to begin the interview process. Interviews are scheduled
to start on May 6th and will take place every Wednesday and Thursday.

So, please share your availability for two rounds of interviews according
to the Wednesday and Thursday schedule mentioned above.

Also, moving forward, your candidature will be managed by Priyanka Biswas.
Priyanka will be your primary point of contact who will guide you through
the upcoming interview process at Google.

It was wonderful connecting with you, and I wish you the best of luck.
Please let me know if you have any questions.

Best regards,



<http://careers.google.com/>

Harish Gumpini

